<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>NextGen Platform</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #141e30, #243b55);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Navigatiebalk */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #00f2ff;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Hoofdsectie */
        .hero {
            height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            max-width: 600px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .main-button {
            padding: 18px 45px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00f2ff, #ff00c8);
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .main-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?autoplay=1" target="_blank">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oHg5SJYRHA0?autoplay=1" target="_blank">Features</a>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?autoplay=1&start=30" target="_blank">Beta</a>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?autoplay=1&start=60" target="_blank">Updates</a>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Welkom bij NextGen</h1>
    <p>Ontdek de nieuwste innovatieve functies van ons platform. Alles is ontworpen voor snelheid, prestaties en ultieme gebruikerservaring.</p>
    <button class="main-button"
        onclick="window.open('https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ?autoplay=1','_blank')">
        Start Nu
    </button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
